import React from 'react'

const CheckoutProduct = () => {
    return (
        <>
            <ProductFlex>
                <ProductImage/>
                <ProductInfo>
                    <ProductTitle>{origin}</ProductTitle>
                    <ProductPrice> </ProductPrice>
                </ProductInfo>
            </ProductFlex>
        </>
    )
}

export default CheckoutProduct
